Interface IntSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Integer>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IntSet.IntSetFromBitSet, IntSet.SingletonIntSet

    public interface IntSet
extends java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Integer>
    Interface for an ordered set of integers that allows efficient (1) iteration (normal and reversed order) and (2) efficient tests of set membership.
    Provides static helpers for wrapping a BitSet or a singleton value.
